---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Card from "../components/ui/card.astro";
import Button from "../components/ui/button.astro";
import Input from "../components/ui/input.astro";
import Checkbox from "../components/ui/checkbox.astro";
import { site } from "../data/site";

const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<Layout
  title={`${site.name} | Manifesto`}
  description="A manifesto for local-first software: tools that run on your device, keep your data private, and work on your terms."
>
  <div class="min-h-screen">
    <header
      class="mx-auto flex max-w-200 items-center justify-between px-6 py-6 sm:px-10"
    >
      <a href="#top" class="font-logo text-xl font-bold">{site.name}</a>
      <nav class="ml-auto flex gap-4" aria-label="Social links">
        {
          site.socialLinks.map((link) => (
            <a
              href={link.href}
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              aria-label={link.ariaLabel}
              class="flex items-center justify-center text-xl transition-colors"
            >
              <i class={link.iconClass} />
            </a>
          ))
        }
      </nav>
    </header>

    <section
      id="top"
      class="mx-auto max-w-300 px-5 pt-10 text-center sm:px-8 sm:pt-14 lg:px-10 lg:pt-16"
    >
      <p
        class="mb-4 font-display text-base italic font-bold text-accent opacity-0 motion-safe:animate-fade-up sm:mb-6 sm:text-lg"
      >
        A note from the maker
      </p>
      <h1
        class="mb-5 font-display text-[clamp(2.5rem,9vw,5rem)] leading-[1.08] text-body opacity-0 motion-safe:animate-fade-up motion-safe:[animation-delay:120ms] sm:mb-6"
      >
        <strong class="text-[clamp(3.1rem,14vw,8rem)] font-black"
          >Your Tools<span class="text-accent">.</span></strong
        ><br />
        <span
          class="mt-3 inline-block text-[clamp(2rem,9vw,5.5rem)] leading-[1.15] sm:mt-5"
          >Your Data<span class="text-accent">.</span> Your Rules<span
            class="text-accent">.</span
          ></span
        >
      </h1>
      <p
        class="mx-auto mt-10 max-w-135 px-2 text-lg leading-[1.7] text-body/60 opacity-0 motion-safe:animate-fade-up motion-safe:[animation-delay:240ms] sm:mt-14 sm:px-0 sm:text-xl lg:mt-16 lg:text-2xl"
      >
        Local-first software that runs on your device. No cloud lock-in. No
        tracking. No nonsense.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section
      id="manifesto"
      class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-200 px-5 pb-14 sm:mt-28 sm:px-8 sm:pb-20 lg:mt-32 lg:px-10 lg:pb-24"
    >
      <div
        class="mx-auto max-w-132 text-base leading-[1.85] text-body opacity-0 motion-safe:animate-fade-up motion-safe:[animation-delay:360ms] sm:text-[1.0625rem] sm:leading-[1.9]"
      >
        <p>Hi, I’m building software tools, and I'm doing it differently.</p>

        <p class="mt-6">
          Most apps today are built backwards.<br />
          They’re “free” because you’re the product.<br />
          They track everything.<br />
          Your data lives on someone else’s server.
        </p>
        <p class="my-6">
          When the internet drops, they stop working. <br /><br />
          I think that’s broken.<br /><br />
          So here’s what I’m building instead:<br />
        </p>

        <div class="my-8 space-y-5 sm:space-y-6">
          <p>
            <strong class="font-bold">Tools that run on your device.</strong><br
            />
            Not in a cloud somewhere. They work offline, locally, under your control.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong class="font-bold">Your data stays yours.</strong><br />
            It lives on your machine. You can move it, export it, delete it. I can't
            see it, sell it, or share it.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong class="font-bold">Privacy by default.</strong><br />
            Analytics are off unless you turn them on. No tracking. No surveillance.
            No hidden data collection.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong class="font-bold">Honest pricing.</strong><br />
            Good tools aren't free. I'll charge fairly so I can build for you - not
            for advertisers.
          </p>
        </div>

        <p class="mb-6">
          That's the deal.<br />Simple tools that respect you. <br /><br /> More apps
          coming soon.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-8 font-display font-medium text-accent">
          - {site.founder}
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section
      class="mx-auto max-w-130 px-5 text-center font-display text-3xl leading-tight font-bold sm:px-8 sm:text-4xl"
    >
      <h2
        class="opacity-0 motion-safe:animate-fade-up motion-safe:[animation-delay:600ms]"
      >
        These beliefs aren’t theoretical. They’re what I’m building toward,
        starting with this:
      </h2>
    </section>

    <section
      id="filer"
      class="mx-auto max-w-180 px-5 py-14 opacity-0 motion-safe:animate-fade-up motion-safe:[animation-delay:720ms] sm:px-8 sm:py-20 lg:px-10 lg:py-24"
    >
      <Card class="border-black/20 bg-[#fdfcfa]">
        <p
          class="mb-3 text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-accent/70"
        >
          Coming soon
        </p>
        <h2 class="mb-4 font-display text-2xl font-bold text-body sm:text-3xl">
          Filer <span class="text-sm font-normal">by Your Tools</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="mb-5 leading-[1.6] text-body/70">
          Building tools takes time. Join the waitlist to know when each one
          launches. No spam - only important updates.
        </p>
        <p>
          <Button href="#waitlist" class="!w-auto"
            >Interested? Join the waitlist</Button
          >
        </p>
      </Card>
    </section>

    <section
      id="waitlist"
      class="mx-auto max-w-130 px-5 leading-tight opacity-0 motion-safe:animate-fade-up motion-safe:[animation-delay:1000ms] sm:px-8"
    >
      <h2 class="text-center font-display text-3xl font-bold sm:text-4xl">
        Are you interested yet?
      </h2>
      <p
        class="mx-auto my-6 max-w-100 text-center leading-[1.6] text-body/70 sm:my-7"
      >
        Building tools takes time. Join the waitlist to know when each one
        launches. <br /><br /> No spam - only important updates.
      </p>
      <form
        class="flex flex-col gap-3"
        data-waitlist-form
        aria-describedby="waitlist-note waitlist-feedback"
      >
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:gap-2">
          <Input
            type="email"
            id="email"
            name="email"
            placeholder="your@email.com"
            autocomplete="email"
            aria-label="Email address"
            required
            class="w-full sm:flex-4/6"
          />
          <Button type="submit" class="w-full sm:flex-2/6">Join waitlist</Button
          >
        </div>
        <label
          class="mt-2 flex items-start justify-center gap-2.5 text-[0.8125rem] leading-[1.5] sm:items-center"
        >
          <Checkbox id="updates" name="updates" />
          I'd also like to follow the journey (blog posts, behind-the-scenes)
        </label>
        <p
          id="waitlist-note"
          class="text-center text-sm leading-[1.6] text-body/55"
        >
          This preview keeps submissions on your device for now. The launch
          email flow goes live with the first product release.
        </p>
        <p
          id="waitlist-feedback"
          class="text-center text-sm leading-[1.6] text-accent"
          data-waitlist-feedback
          aria-live="polite"
        >
        </p>
      </form>
    </section>

    <footer
      class="mt-24 mb-12 px-5 opacity-0 motion-safe:animate-fade-up motion-safe:[animation-delay:1250ms] sm:mt-32 sm:mb-16 sm:px-8 lg:mt-36 lg:mb-20"
    >
      <div
        class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 text-center sm:flex-row sm:gap-5 sm:divide-x-2 sm:divide-body/20"
      >
        <p class="font-logo text-2xl font-bold sm:pr-5">{site.name}</p>
        <p class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:gap-5">
          {
            site.socialLinks.map((link) => (
              <a
                href={link.href}
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                aria-label={link.ariaLabel}
                class="flex items-center justify-center transition-colors"
              >
                <i class={`${link.iconClass} mr-1`} />
                <span>{link.label}</span>
              </a>
            ))
          }
        </p>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-4 text-center text-xs opacity-70">
        © {currentYear}
        {site.name} • Built by {site.founder}
      </p>
    </footer>
  </div>
</Layout>

<script is:inline>
  const storageKey = "your-tools-waitlist-preview";
  const form = document.querySelector("[data-waitlist-form]");
  const feedback = document.querySelector("[data-waitlist-feedback]");

  if (form instanceof HTMLFormElement && feedback instanceof HTMLElement) {
    let submissions = JSON.parse(
      window.localStorage.getItem(storageKey) ?? "[]",
    );

    if (submissions.length > 0) {
      feedback.textContent =
        "You are already saved on this device. We will wire up email delivery before launch.";
    }

    form.addEventListener("submit", (event) => {
      event.preventDefault();

      const formData = new FormData(form);
      const email = String(formData.get("email") ?? "")
        .trim()
        .toLowerCase();
      const updates = formData.get("updates") === "on";

      if (!email) {
        feedback.textContent = "Enter an email address to save your interest.";
        return;
      }

      const nextSubmissions = submissions.filter(
        (entry) => entry.email !== email,
      );

      nextSubmissions.push({
        email,
        updates,
        createdAt: new Date().toISOString(),
      });

      submissions = nextSubmissions;
      window.localStorage.setItem(storageKey, JSON.stringify(nextSubmissions));

      feedback.textContent =
        "Saved on this device. Email delivery will be connected before the first product ships.";
      form.reset();
    });
  }
</script>
